      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just been a few days though and the shaking is getting kind of bad. i read online that drinking way more water can help keep levels stable. should i just try to double my water intake and see if that fixes the nausea? also do u think it's worth waiting a week to see if it goes away before i call the clinic?",
