      "content": "okay i'll call them tomorrow then. i been feeling a bit dizzy too, like maybe my blood pressure is just low from the meds? honestly i hate going to the clinic for every little thing and it's kinda expensive so i was also thinking maybe i could just take an extra dose of my vitamin b next time i feel shaky to see if that helps stabilize me instead of dealing with the doctor right now?",
